						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up near the dilapidated temple of Vighneśvara.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Paridhāvi, Kārttika ba. 2, Thursday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records contain concessions granted to farmers <hi rend="italic">(Kāṁpu)</hi> of Gurijāla by <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Tirumalarāja Veṅgaḷarājadēva. In characters of about the 16th century A.D.</p>						

